### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@userToken = your-user-token-here
@comptableToken = your-comptable-token-here
@adminToken = your-admin-token-here

### ==================== DOCUMENT RETRIEVAL ====================

### Get All Documents for Current User's Societes (paginated + filtered)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Get All Documents - With Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents?statut=EN_ATTENTE&typeDocument=FACTURE_ACHAT&exerciceComptable=2024&page=0&size=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Get Pending Documents for Current User
# ADMIN    → returns all pending documents platform-wide
# COMPTABLE → returns pending documents for assigned societes only
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Documents By Fiscal Year (Exercice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/exercice/2024
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Get Document By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Download Document By ID (returns file as attachment)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/download
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### ==================== DOCUMENT UPLOAD ====================

### Upload Document - FACTURE_ACHAT (requires fournisseur)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="facture-001.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./facture-001.pdf
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="societeId"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="numeroPiece"

FAC-ACHAT-001
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="typeDocument"

FACTURE_ACHAT
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="categorieComptable"

ACHAT
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="datePiece"

2024-06-01
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="montant"

1500.00
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="fournisseur"

Fournisseur XYZ
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="exerciceComptable"

2024
--boundary--

