### ==================== VALIDATION (ADMIN ONLY) ====================

### Validate Document - Approve
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "VALIDER",
  "commentaire": "Document conforme aux exigences comptables"
}

### Validate Document - Reject (commentaire is required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "REJETER",
  "commentaire": "Erreur sur le montant indiqué"
}

### ==================== AUDIT LOGS (ADMIN ONLY) ====================

### Get Audit Trail for a Document
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==================== ERROR CASES ====================

### Upload - Missing societeId (should fail - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="facture.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./facture.pdf
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="numeroPiece"

FAC-ERR-NO-SOCIETE
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="typeDocument"

FACTURE_VENTE
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="categorieComptable"

VENTE
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="datePiece"

2024-06-01
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="montant"

500.00
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="exerciceComptable"

2024
--boundary--

