### Validate Without Token (should fail - 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "VALIDER",
  "commentaire": "Sans authentification"
}

### Validate With Non-Admin Token (should fail - 403 ACCESS_DENIED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "VALIDER",
  "commentaire": "Tentative sans droits admin"
}

### Reject Without Comment (should fail - 400 REJECTION_REASON_REQUIRED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "REJETER"
}

### Validate Already Processed Document (should fail - 400 ALREADY_PROCESSED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "VALIDER",
  "commentaire": "Re-validation attempt"
}

### Get Audit Logs With Non-Admin Token (should fail - 403 ACCESS_DENIED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### ==================== SOFT DELETE ====================

### Soft Delete - Pending Document (any authenticated user, marks as SUPPRIME)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Soft Delete - Rejected Document (ADMIN only, marks as SUPPRIME)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Soft Delete - Rejected Document With Non-Admin Token (should fail - 403 FORBIDDEN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/2
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}

### Soft Delete - Validated Document (should fail - 400 NOT_DELETABLE)
# Validated documents cannot be soft-deleted — use purge after soft-deleting a SUPPRIME doc
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Soft Delete - Already SUPPRIME Document (should fail - 400 ALREADY_DELETED)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==================== PURGE (PERMANENT / HARD DELETE - ADMIN ONLY) ====================

### Purge - SUPPRIME Document (ADMIN only, clears audit logs + deletes file + deletes record)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/purge
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Purge - Non-SUPPRIME Document (should fail - 400 PURGE_NOT_ALLOWED)
# Document must have SUPPRIME status before it can be purged
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/3/purge
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Purge - With Non-Admin Token (should fail - 403 ACCESS_DENIED)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/1/purge
Authorization: Bearer {{comptableToken}}
